Class RangedConstraint<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.validate.option.FieldConstraint<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - value of the option
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Constraint
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MaxConstraint, MinConstraint, RangeConstraint

    @Immutable
public abstract class RangedConstraint<T>
extends FieldConstraint<T>
    A constraint that puts a numeric field value into a range.

    A field which violates this constraint of its value is out of the range.
